OL,3,CFormer Premier League referee David
OL,4,CCoote's sentencing delayed
OL,6,FThe sentencing of former Premier
OL,7,FLeague referee David Coote over a
OL,8,Fchild abuse video found on his device
OL,9,Fhas been delayed until next month.
OL,11,FCoote, 43, pleaded guilty to making an
OL,12,Findecent image of a child, at a court
OL,13,Fhearing in October, after a category A
OL,14,Fvideo, the most serious kind, was
OL,15,Fdiscovered by police.
OL,17,FHe was due to appear at Nottingham
OL,18,FCrown Court on Thursday for sentence
OL,19,Fbut it was adjourned to January 8
OL,20,Fbecause his barrister could not attend
OL,21,Ffor medical reasons.
