OL,3,CFormer Premier League referee David
OL,4,CCoote's sentencing delayed
OL,6,FJudge Nirmal Shant KC said she was
OL,7,F"simply not prepared" to deal with the
OL,8,Fsentencing if his lawyer appeared in
OL,9,Fcourt by video-link.
OL,11,FCoote, of Woodhill Road in Collingham,
OL,12,Fnear Newark, Nottinghamshire, did not
OL,13,Fattend court for the three-minute
OL,14,Fhearing to reschedule the sentencing.
OL,16,FThe offence of making an indecent
OL,17,Fimage of a child refers to activities
OL,18,Fsuch as downloading, sharing or saving
OL,19,Fabuse photos or videos.
