OL,3,CFormer Premier League referee David
OL,4,CCoote's sentencing delayed
OL,6,FAn earlier magistrates' court hearing
OL,7,Fwas told the video came to the
OL,8,Fpolice's attention after the Football
OL,9,FAssociation's investigation into Coote.
OL,11,FA number of devices were seized and
OL,12,Fanalysed when Coote was arrested at
OL,13,Fhis home, and the video was then
OL,14,Ffound, the court had heard.
OL,16,FCoote was sacked by Professional Game
OL,17,FMatch Officials Limited in December
OL,18,Fafter a video of comments he had made
OL,19,Fabout former Liverpool boss Jurgen
OL,20,FKlopp in 2020 came to light.
