OL,3,CFormer Premier League referee David
OL,4,CCoote's sentencing delayed
OL,6,FIn August this year he was given an
OL,7,Feight-week suspension by the Football
OL,8,FAssociation over the Klopp footage.
OL,10,FThe former referee came out as gay in
OL,11,Fan interview with The Sun in January
OL,12,Fand said a lifelong struggle to hide
OL,13,Fhis sexuality had contributed to the
OL,14,Frant about Klopp.
